Package: alkahest
Title: Pre-Processing XY Data from Experimental Methods
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Nicolas",
             family = "Frerebeau",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "nicolas.frerebeau@u-bordeaux-montaigne.fr",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5759-4944", 
                         affiliation = "Universit√© Bordeaux Montaigne")))
Maintainer: Nicolas Frerebeau <nicolas.frerebeau@u-bordeaux-montaigne.fr>
Description: A toolbox for pre-processing XY data from experimental methods 
    (i.e. any signal that can be measured along a continuous variable). This 
    package provides methods for baseline correction, smoothing, normalization 
    and integration.
